body_html:
@wangyongqi
The error message was "Unrecognized option: --input_file".
However, according to the official tutorial, it seems that you specified a .pb file with the option "--graph_def_file".
By the way, the official tutorial is not a "toco" binary.
I do not know the type of script you solved, but it was good that the problem was resolved.
